title: Alabama Wideout Jameson Williams Hurt in National Title Game
description: Jameson Williams went to a tent on the sideline before heading into the locker room during the second quarter of the national championship game.
dc:creator: Alanis Thames
media:credit: AJ Mast for The New York Times
media:description: Alabama wide receiver Jameson Williams holding his left knee after making a long catch in the second quarter.
